com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.annotations

Class MarkerOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.annotations.BaseMarkerOptions<Marker,MarkerOptions>
      • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.annotations.MarkerOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    Deprecated. 
    As of 7.0.0, use Mapbox Annotation Plugin instead

    @Deprecated
public final class MarkerOptions
extends BaseMarkerOptions<Marker,MarkerOptions>
implements android.os.Parcelable

    Builder for composing Marker objects. See Marker for additional information.

    Example

     mapView.addMarker(new MarkerOptions()
   .title("Intersection")
   .snippet("H St NW with 15th St NW")
   .position(new LatLng(38.9002073, -77.03364419)));
